{
  "texts": [
    "This scenario presents the worst-case scenario, serving as a cautionary tale and emphasizing the need for balanced, responsible use of GenAI tools in education to preserve the integrity and effectiveness of the learning experience.",
    "In this scenario, despite the availability of GenAI as a valuable educational resource, students opt to use it sparingly and, when in use, in an inappropriate manner.",
    "Rather than leveraging the tool for its intended purpose of assisting in the learning process, it is predominantly utilized for shortcuts, such as committing plagiarism or seeking immediate answers without genuine comprehension (Lo, 2023).",
    "This minimal engagement with GenAI leads to missed opportunities.",
    "It becomes necessary for educators to teach how to use the technology appropriately."
  ]
}